  }, "v2"), mdx("p", null, "\xCA-ti\xEAn \u0111\xE1p, \"Th\u01B0a c\xE1c anh v\xE0 c\xE1c cha, xin nghe t\xF4i n\xF3i. Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF vinh hi\u1EC3n c\u1EE7a ch\xFAng ta hi\u1EC7n ra c\xF9ng \xC1p-ra-ham, t\u1ED5 ti\xEAn c\u1EE7a ch\xFAng ta \u1EDF M\xEA-s\xF4-b\xF4-ta-mi tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi \xF4ng \u0111\u1EBFn sinh s\u1ED1ng t\u1EA1i Ha-ran. "), mdx("h6", {
