  }, "v5"), mdx("p", null, "Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF kh\xF4ng cho \xF4ng ph\u1EA7n \u0111\u1EA5t n\xE0o \u1EDF \u0111\xE2y c\u1EA3, d\xF9 l\xE0 mi\u1EBFng \u0111\u1EA5t b\u1EB1ng b\xE0n ch\xE2n \u0111i n\u1EEFa. Nh\u01B0ng Ng\xE0i h\u1EE9a s\u1EBD c\u1EA5p cho \xF4ng c\xF9ng d\xF2ng d\xF5i \xF4ng \u0111\u1EA5t n\u1EA7y, ngay tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi \xC1p-ra-ham c\xF3 con. "), mdx("h6", {
