  }, "v26"), mdx("p", null, "H\xF4m sau \xF4ng th\u1EA5y hai ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \xCDt-ra-en \u0111\xE1nh nhau, M\xF4-se t\xECm c\xE1ch can ng\u0103n h\u1ECD v\xE0 b\u1EA3o h\u1ECD, 'N\u1EA7y, ch\xFAng ta l\xE0 anh em. T\u1EA1i sao l\u1EA1i h\u1EA1i nhau nh\u01B0 v\u1EADy?' "), mdx("h6", {
