  }, "v28"), mdx("p", null, "Hay anh mu\u1ED1n gi\u1EBFt t\xF4i nh\u01B0 \u0111\xE3 gi\u1EBFt ng\u01B0\u1EDDi Ai-c\u1EADp h\xF4m qua sao?' "), mdx("h6", {
