    "id": "v36"
  }, "v36"), mdx("p", null, "M\xF4-se d\u1EABn d\xE2n ch\xFAng ra kh\u1ECFi Ai-c\u1EADp. \xD4ng l\xE0m nhi\u1EC1u ph\xE9p l\u1EA1 v\xE0 d\u1EA5u k\u1EF3 t\u1EA1i Ai-c\u1EADp, n\u01A1i H\u1ED3ng h\u1EA3i v\xE0 trong sa m\u1EA1c su\u1ED1t b\u1ED1n m\u01B0\u01A1i n\u0103m. "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v37"
  }, "v37"), mdx("p", null, "C\u0169ng ch\xEDnh M\xF4-se n\u1EA7y l\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\xE3 b\u1EA3o d\xE2n \xCDt-ra-en r\u1EB1ng 'Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF s\u1EBD ch\u1ECDn m\u1ED9t nh\xE0 ti\xEAn tri nh\u01B0 ta t\u1EEB trong v\xF2ng c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i.' "), mdx("h6", {
